message: "If you use this repository, code, saved models, or LAADAN-AC implementation, please cite this work."
title: "Lagrangian Admissibility-Aware Deep Action-Nudging Actor-Critic for Safer ICU-Sepsis Treatment Decisions"
type: software
authors:
